1
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:35,980
[Zhan Zhao Adventures]

2
00:01:35,980 --> 00:01:37,980
[Episode 3]

3
00:02:10,550 --> 00:02:11,090
Just now,

4
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:14,210
your fight with Jiao Chaogui

5
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:16,490
was truly impressive.

6
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,620
I misjudged you.

7
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,340
Why didn't you explain yourself?

8
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:24,650
I told you before.

9
00:02:25,790 --> 00:02:26,810
I have too many enemies.

10
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,020
You'd be safer

11
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,770
traveling with him alone.

12
00:02:31,070 --> 00:02:33,140
If we hadn't made it back in time,

13
00:02:33,510 --> 00:02:34,140
you could've died

14
00:02:34,140 --> 00:02:35,300
covering for us

15
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,270
at the hands of Jiao Chaogui.

16
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,020
Do you realize that?

17
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:40,980
In your mind,

18
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,890
are you the only one who can protect us?

19
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:43,820
And we can't protect you?

20
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,420
That's not what I meant.

21
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,730
Just because I'm new to the martial world

22
00:02:59,730 --> 00:03:00,590
doesn't mean I'm clueless.

23
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,210
Out here in the martial world,

24
00:03:02,350 --> 00:03:03,700
who doesn't have enemies?

25
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:06,170
That Jiao Chaogui just now

26
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,730
came after me with a sword formation.

27
00:03:08,790 --> 00:03:10,170
He's obviously one of my enemies.

28
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:12,050
Stop making everything

29
00:03:12,350 --> 00:03:13,570
about yourself,

30
00:03:13,570 --> 00:03:14,490
like you're the only one with enemies.

31
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,020
I didn't mean that either.

32
00:03:22,950 --> 00:03:23,700
I say

33
00:03:23,790 --> 00:03:24,530
on this journey,

34
00:03:24,530 --> 00:03:25,330
let's help each other

35
00:03:25,330 --> 00:03:26,100
deal with

36
00:03:26,130 --> 00:03:26,980
each other's enemies.

37
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,860
That way, neither of us gets the upper hand.

38
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:32,890
Well said, Huo.

39
00:03:33,950 --> 00:03:34,610
You've got a point.

40
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,380
What really happened to your injury?

41
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,700
I didn't want to drag you into this.

42
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:51,340
We've already

43
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:52,910
been through life and death together.

44
00:03:53,790 --> 00:03:55,100
So why are you still hiding things from me?

45
00:03:58,350 --> 00:03:59,330
I had an old friend.

46
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,930
He was a constable in Yicheng County.

47
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:03,330
He uncovered a major case

48
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:04,380
and was hunted for it.

49
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:05,890
My injury happened

50
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,020
while I was trying to save him.

51
00:04:08,670 --> 00:04:09,770
Did you save him?

52
00:04:12,510 --> 00:04:13,420
Before he died,

53
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,210
he entrusted the case to me.

54
00:04:16,670 --> 00:04:18,410
I can't betray his final wish.

55
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:34,090
This Xiuluo Cult

56
00:04:34,350 --> 00:04:35,530
has always done evil.

57
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,300
For them,

58
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:38,400
doing evil is routine.

59
00:04:38,910 --> 00:04:39,800
But the Shangqing Sect,

60
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,970
why are they after you?

61
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,290
The one who injured me

62
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,970
wasn't from the Shangqing Sect.

63
00:04:45,910 --> 00:04:47,290
It was the Black Fox Demon, Zhi Hua.

64
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:48,290
That's impossible.

65
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,740
The Great Mercy Palm

66
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:51,020
is the Shangqing Sect's secret art.

67
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,450
Even their disciples

68
00:04:53,450 --> 00:04:54,890
might never learn the true technique.

69
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:56,500
Besides, their palm technique

70
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:57,820
has always been passed down orally.

71
00:04:57,910 --> 00:04:58,820
There are no manuals for it.

72
00:04:59,910 --> 00:05:01,260
Outsiders couldn't have stolen it.

73
00:05:01,550 --> 00:05:03,260
I can't figure it out either.

74
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:10,850
Forget it.

75
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,210
I'll trust you for now.

76
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:13,650
But you still have questions.

77
00:05:14,550 --> 00:05:15,500
But I also know

78
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:16,970
it wasn't easy for you

79
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:17,850
to tell me all that.

80
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:19,940
Since I know you're not a bad person,

81
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:20,850
let's leave it at that.

82
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,330
So are we friends now?

83
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,540
Let's wait

84
00:05:30,540 --> 00:05:31,580
until he settles his business.

85
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:32,210
Then we'll see.

86
00:05:32,910 --> 00:05:33,530
For now,

87
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:36,180
we're just traveling together.

88
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,650
Traveling together

89
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,650
to the capital.

90
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:01,180
What are you thinking about, Huo?

91
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,180
I'm wondering

92
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,470
why Shengyun Manor

93
00:06:03,470 --> 00:06:04,980
has a sword formation

94
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,740
specifically made to counter Linglong Manor.

95
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,330
Jiao Chaogui wouldn't tell me why.

96
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,700
There has to be a scheme behind it.

97
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:12,850
The reason behind it

98
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:14,140
might be very simple.

99
00:06:14,990 --> 00:06:15,620
So simple

100
00:06:16,230 --> 00:06:16,940
that only someone

101
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,090
as pure-hearted as you

102
00:06:18,350 --> 00:06:19,210
would fail to see it.

103
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:21,530
In the martial world,

104
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:22,740
there are three great manors.

105
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,330
Golden Bawang,

106
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,140
Silver Shengyun,

107
00:06:25,550 --> 00:06:26,210
and Jade Linglong.

108
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:27,740
Bawang Manor

109
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:29,140
fell into decline ten years ago.

110
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,850
So you're saying all that research

111
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,190
was done to seize

112
00:06:33,220 --> 00:06:34,260
the title of top manor in the world?

113
00:06:36,110 --> 00:06:36,940
He lost to you,

114
00:06:37,470 --> 00:06:38,260
so he couldn't exactly

115
00:06:38,350 --> 00:06:39,850
keep talking about rivaling Linglong Manor.

116
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,020
So he brushed it off instead.

117
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,090
Years of painstaking research...

118
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:45,780
If I hadn't stumbled upon it

119
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:46,580
and broken the sword formation,

120
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:48,650
Linglong Manor

121
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:49,940
might've faced disaster.

122
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,380
Don't worry, Huo.

123
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,970
The master of Linglong Manor

124
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:53,970
has probably long figured out

125
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,890
what Shengyun Manor is after.

126
00:06:55,550 --> 00:06:56,700
He won't just sit back and wait for disaster.

127
00:06:59,030 --> 00:07:00,210
I heard before

128
00:07:00,210 --> 00:07:01,370
that Bawang Manor fell

129
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:03,730
because they challenged

130
00:07:03,730 --> 00:07:04,660
the Linyuan Sect.

131
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,710
In the end, the entire sect was wiped out.

132
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,500
The lesson is right there.

133
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:09,890
I really don't know

134
00:07:09,890 --> 00:07:10,830
why Shengyun Manor still insists on fighting.

135
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,020
Aren't they afraid

136
00:07:12,110 --> 00:07:13,060
of ending up the same way?

137
00:07:13,550 --> 00:07:14,700
Before Bawang Manor was destroyed,

138
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:16,770
it once stood glorious

139
00:07:16,870 --> 00:07:17,850
as the top manor in the world.

140
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,530
When people in the martial world fight,

141
00:07:20,990 --> 00:07:22,450
only the winners are remembered.

142
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:24,140
That's why Jiao Chaogui

143
00:07:24,230 --> 00:07:25,260
can't accept his defeat.

144
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:27,430
Wasn't martial arts meant to protect ourselves

145
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:28,390
and uphold justice?

146
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,410
Fighting all day long,

147
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:31,890
you win today, I win tomorrow...

148
00:07:32,350 --> 00:07:33,060
What's the point of it all?

149
00:07:33,670 --> 00:07:35,090
Once you've spent more time in the martial world,

150
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:36,450
Huo,

151
00:07:36,790 --> 00:07:37,700
you'll get used to it.

152
00:07:38,230 --> 00:07:39,650
If I end up thinking like them,

153
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,500
I might as well go home right now.

154
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,820
I wish I could be like you.

155
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,300
You understand everything,

156
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,620
but nothing seems to bother you.

157
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:57,060
Let's find a tea stand

158
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:57,970
and take a break.

159
00:08:59,900 --> 00:09:03,940
[Granny Hanshui, Master of Hanshui Palace]

160
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:17,100
Changhong Jade,

161
00:09:17,670 --> 00:09:18,770
I've been

162
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,500
waiting for you a long time.

163
00:09:22,590 --> 00:09:24,170
Granny came herself to get you.

164
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,290
Now come here.

165
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:28,170
His name isn't Changhong Jade.

166
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,530
And he's not going back with you.

167
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,620
Where'd this brat come from?

168
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,460
Move aside now.

169
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,380
I will make sure

170
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,050
they leave your body intact.

171
00:09:39,950 --> 00:09:40,810
You want to take him?

172
00:09:41,590 --> 00:09:42,530
Kill me first.

173
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:50,290
No!

174
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,220
So you're a kid from the Huo family.

175
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:54,740
So young,

176
00:09:54,830 --> 00:09:56,260
and already quite skilled.

177
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:57,500
What a pity.

178
00:10:06,590 --> 00:10:07,260
Moon Envoy,

179
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:10,170
this is the one you mentioned?

180
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,220
That's him.

181
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,690
Faster than my cane?

182
00:10:14,430 --> 00:10:15,690
Interesting.

183
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:28,260
You're not just badly injured.

184
00:10:28,710 --> 00:10:30,140
You've also been poisoned.

185
00:10:31,070 --> 00:10:33,050
You still want to fight a losing battle?

186
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:33,890
Zhan!

187
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:37,770
The poison in your body...

188
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:39,740
there's no cure for it at all.

189
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:40,620
The medicinal effect

190
00:10:40,710 --> 00:10:41,740
in my blood is already gone,

191
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:42,740
right?

192
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:44,570
You already knew.

193
00:10:47,430 --> 00:10:48,770
You were born unable to speak,

194
00:10:49,590 --> 00:10:51,170
but slowly regained your voice.

195
00:10:51,830 --> 00:10:52,620
The medicinal scent on you

196
00:10:53,310 --> 00:10:54,650
has also grown weaker each day.

197
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:57,020
I'm useless now.

198
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,530
Why didn't you tell me?

199
00:11:01,950 --> 00:11:02,770
Without that medicinal effect,

200
00:11:04,070 --> 00:11:05,220
you can finally live as a real person.

201
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:27,530
Zhan!

202
00:11:29,830 --> 00:11:30,690
Sun Envoy, Moon Envoy.

203
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,570
Kill them both

204
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:33,810
and take Changhong Jade away.

205
00:11:34,430 --> 00:11:34,860
Granny.

206
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:35,770
What?

207
00:11:36,190 --> 00:11:37,020
Feeling soft-hearted?

208
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:38,170
I wouldn't dare.

209
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:39,100
Do it.

210
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:46,770
Stop!

211
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:52,930
Granny,

212
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:53,930
I'll go back with you.

213
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:55,690
Just spare the two of them.

214
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:56,460
No!

215
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:58,890
The secret of Changhong Jade can't get out.

216
00:11:59,190 --> 00:12:00,460
These two must die.

217
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:02,460
If they die,

218
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:03,460
I won't keep living either.

219
00:12:04,190 --> 00:12:05,280
Then you'll never get

220
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:06,020
Changhong Jade.

221
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,560
You've gotten bold.

222
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:09,380
You dare threaten me now?

223
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:10,320
To save them,

224
00:12:10,650 --> 00:12:11,620
I'll do anything!

225
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,410
These two?

226
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:15,530
They're worth risking your life for?

227
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,810
You must think

228
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:18,220
that Su Yizhou

229
00:12:18,310 --> 00:12:19,570
forced me to leave.

230
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:20,460
Don't tell me

231
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:21,810
you went with him

232
00:12:21,910 --> 00:12:23,050
of your own free will?

233
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,530
I chose to leave on my own.

234
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,890
Su Yizhou once predicted

235
00:12:26,890 --> 00:12:27,890
that I'd die at fifteen.

236
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,100
When I know

237
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:31,290
no matter how hard I struggle to survive,

238
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:32,890
and I still won't live long,

239
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:35,530
of course I'd want to see the outside world.

240
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:37,220
So,

241
00:12:37,910 --> 00:12:39,890
while you were in secluded cultivation,

242
00:12:40,590 --> 00:12:41,630
I tricked

243
00:12:41,630 --> 00:12:42,500
the two guard dogs at the gate

244
00:12:42,830 --> 00:12:43,460
and escaped the palace.

245
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:45,050
Well then,

246
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:47,650
is the outside world beautiful?

247
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:51,380
Ever since I left Hanshui Palace,

248
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,810
people have fought over me

249
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:54,500
and abused me.

250
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:56,100
Only those two

251
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:57,140
treated me like a person.

252
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,340
They protected me like treasure

253
00:12:58,550 --> 00:12:59,980
and never coveted my secret.

254
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,170
If someone in this world

255
00:13:02,590 --> 00:13:03,770
is willing to die for me,

256
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,100
then I'd gladly

257
00:13:06,310 --> 00:13:07,140
give my life for them too.

258
00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:09,770
After you die,

259
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,650
I can always find

260
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:12,860
a new Changhong Jade.

261
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,530
With your abilities,

262
00:13:15,190 --> 00:13:16,980
finding another won't be hard.

263
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:20,190
But every four months,

264
00:13:20,190 --> 00:13:21,820
you need my help

265
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:23,650
to continue cultivating the Luotian Art.

266
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,530
By my count,

267
00:13:25,760 --> 00:13:26,930
it's been

268
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,460
over three months since last time.

269
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:31,430
When the critical moment comes,

270
00:13:31,430 --> 00:13:32,740
without my help,

271
00:13:32,830 --> 00:13:33,620
I imagine

272
00:13:33,710 --> 00:13:35,280
you'll need another ten,

273
00:13:35,450 --> 00:13:37,170
maybe twenty years to make a breakthrough.

274
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,830
Can you really wait that long?

275
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:40,650
Besides,

276
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:42,380
if Changhong Jade were so easy to find,

277
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:43,930
you wouldn't have come

278
00:13:44,040 --> 00:13:45,570
all the way out to this wilderness yourself.

279
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:01,650
Fine,

280
00:14:03,430 --> 00:14:04,980
I'll agree to your terms.

281
00:14:17,230 --> 00:14:18,100
I didn't expect

282
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:19,660
a child like you

283
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:21,660
to be both bold and sharp.

284
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:23,860
You've got courage and brains.

285
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:28,090
I truly underestimated you.

286
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:33,500
♪Once I entered the mortal world with my sword...♪

287
00:14:33,590 --> 00:14:34,410
You can't go back.

288
00:14:35,430 --> 00:14:37,300
You're the first person who ever cried for me.

289
00:14:38,640 --> 00:14:39,540
In this world,

290
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:42,580
someone actually cried for me.

291
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:45,050
That already makes me luckier than most.

292
00:14:47,470 --> 00:14:48,020
Don't go.

293
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:51,540
The outside world

294
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,450
may be dangerous,

295
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:54,810
but the people I care about are there.

296
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:56,620
One day,

297
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,900
I'll leave Hanshui Palace.

298
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,490
One day,

299
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:00,810
I'll find you again.

300
00:15:00,820 --> 00:15:02,860
♪Slowly losing my way back♪

301
00:15:03,060 --> 00:15:09,140
♪Yet my heart remains unchanged♪

302
00:15:10,300 --> 00:15:14,980
♪Once I step into the martial world...♪

303
00:15:16,760 --> 00:15:17,980
Your real name

304
00:15:18,070 --> 00:15:19,260
isn't actually Huo Xiaodi.

305
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:21,340
From now on,

306
00:15:21,590 --> 00:15:23,210
can you give that name to me?

307
00:15:27,230 --> 00:15:27,770
That's great,

308
00:15:28,310 --> 00:15:29,340
I have a name again.

309
00:15:29,780 --> 00:15:34,740
♪Let others drift with the tide♪

310
00:15:35,180 --> 00:15:39,820
♪I'll sail against the current♪

311
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:41,980
[Changhong Jade]

312
00:15:42,700 --> 00:15:44,340
[Huo Xiaodi]

313
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:50,620
♪Youthful spirit never fades♪

314
00:15:52,060 --> 00:15:56,860
♪No need to look back today♪

315
00:15:57,180 --> 00:16:01,820
♪Bearing heavy debts and grudges♪

316
00:16:02,220 --> 00:16:06,500
♪Far away, far away♪

317
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:14,260
♪Beneath endless skies and seas♪

318
00:16:14,700 --> 00:16:20,460
♪Far away, far away♪

319
00:16:21,220 --> 00:16:28,820
♪Beneath endless skies and seas♪

320
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:35,700
You're awake.

321
00:16:48,070 --> 00:16:49,140
Changhong Jade...

322
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:51,280
He's called Huo Xiaodi now.

323
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:58,010
I gave him my name.

324
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:01,140
To save us,

325
00:17:01,140 --> 00:17:02,350
he went back

326
00:17:02,350 --> 00:17:02,820
with the people from Hanshui Palace.

327
00:17:03,680 --> 00:17:04,940
We still couldn't save him.

328
00:17:05,630 --> 00:17:06,900
Once I finish what I need to do,

329
00:17:07,590 --> 00:17:08,290
we'll go

330
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:09,700
to Hanshui Palace together.

331
00:17:10,110 --> 00:17:11,860
But rescuing someone from Granny Hanshui

332
00:17:11,860 --> 00:17:12,570
is easier said than done.

333
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:17,050
We'll find a way.

334
00:17:24,150 --> 00:17:26,020
The more I think about it,

335
00:17:28,350 --> 00:17:29,700
For hundreds of years, Hanshui Palace

336
00:17:29,700 --> 00:17:31,370
has rarely been involved in martial world conflicts.

337
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:34,090
Even if Changhong Jade is highly coveted,

338
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:36,320
Granny Hanshui's reputation alone

339
00:17:36,320 --> 00:17:37,370
keeps people from provoking her.

340
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:39,790
So why are the Tang Clan

341
00:17:39,790 --> 00:17:40,850
and Shengyun Manor both after it now?

342
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,040
How did they know

343
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:44,220
when Granny Hanshui would be in

344
00:17:44,310 --> 00:17:45,050
secluded cultivation?

345
00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:46,420
With the strength

346
00:17:46,550 --> 00:17:47,530
of Shengyun Manor and the Tang Clan,

347
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:49,660
they would never

348
00:17:49,760 --> 00:17:51,180
dare storm Hanshui Palace head-on.

349
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:53,370
So this secret

350
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:55,530
must've leaked from inside Hanshui Palace.

351
00:17:57,350 --> 00:17:58,260
Su Yizhou?

352
00:17:59,110 --> 00:18:00,190
While you were unconscious,

353
00:18:00,190 --> 00:18:01,190
Xiaodi mentioned him.

354
00:18:01,190 --> 00:18:02,370
This Su Yizhou...

355
00:18:02,760 --> 00:18:03,420
he said

356
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,760
Su Yizhou predicted

357
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:06,730
that he wouldn't live past fifteen.

358
00:18:07,390 --> 00:18:08,940
That's why he chose to see the outside world.

359
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:13,420
Su Yizhou was known as the greatest fortune teller alive.

360
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:14,570
Rumor has it

361
00:18:15,150 --> 00:18:16,330
he could glimpse the secrets of heaven.

362
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:20,180
But...

363
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:23,050
he died three years ago.

364
00:18:24,350 --> 00:18:25,020
Bawang Manor

365
00:18:25,110 --> 00:18:26,700
went to war with the Linyuan Sect

366
00:18:27,350 --> 00:18:29,130
because Su Yizhou once predicted

367
00:18:30,070 --> 00:18:30,700
that Bawang Manor

368
00:18:31,150 --> 00:18:32,530
would be destroyed by the Linyuan Sect.

369
00:18:33,550 --> 00:18:35,260
The manor lord could neither sleep nor eat.

370
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:36,610
In the end,

371
00:18:36,870 --> 00:18:37,940
he chose to strike first.

372
00:18:38,630 --> 00:18:39,050
But in the end,

373
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:40,850
the entire manor was slaughtered.

374
00:18:42,390 --> 00:18:43,570
The manor lord believed

375
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:45,980
Su Yizhou had provoked the conflict.

376
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:47,180
With his dying breath,

377
00:18:47,180 --> 00:18:47,940
he tracked him down.

378
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:49,460
Su Yizhou's wife

379
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:51,530
died protecting him.

380
00:18:51,531 --> 00:18:57,255
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

381
00:18:52,280 --> 00:18:53,050
After that,

382
00:18:53,150 --> 00:18:54,900
Su Yizhou lost his mind.

383
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:56,050
He kept telling everyone

384
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:57,810
that he never knew fortune-telling at all.

385
00:18:58,790 --> 00:18:59,260
Otherwise,

386
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,130
how could he fail to foresee

387
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,260
his own wife's fate?

388
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:05,200
Then who was the one impersonating Su Yizhou?

389
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:05,770
Who could it be?

390
00:19:06,070 --> 00:19:07,220
Someone who dared enter Hanshui Palace

391
00:19:07,390 --> 00:19:08,610
and deceive Granny Hanshui

392
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:10,130
must have been confident

393
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,740
of escaping unscathed.

394
00:19:12,310 --> 00:19:12,940
And they'd need

395
00:19:13,040 --> 00:19:14,660
masterful disguise skills.

396
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:17,570
Disguise skills...

397
00:19:21,390 --> 00:19:23,290
could it be the ever-changing Black Fox Demon,

398
00:19:23,390 --> 00:19:23,980
Zhi Hua?

399
00:19:26,040 --> 00:19:26,850
Him again.

400
00:19:28,110 --> 00:19:29,290
He lured out Changhong Jade,

401
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,570
then provoked Shengyun Manor and the Tang Clan.

402
00:19:31,570 --> 00:19:32,450
What is he really after?

403
00:19:32,790 --> 00:19:33,900
Using methods like this

404
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:35,130
to pit two factions against each other

405
00:19:35,140 --> 00:19:36,090
seems far too roundabout.

406
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:37,530
Maybe

407
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,220
that wasn't his true goal.

408
00:19:40,070 --> 00:19:41,180
Maybe he just wanted

409
00:19:41,280 --> 00:19:43,130
Hanshui Palace to lose its treasure

410
00:19:43,290 --> 00:19:44,610
so he could strike against them.

411
00:19:45,150 --> 00:19:46,460
Does he have a grudge against Hanshui Palace?

412
00:19:46,790 --> 00:19:47,740
Whether he does or not,

413
00:19:48,350 --> 00:19:48,850
now

414
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:50,850
that Changhong Jade is back in Hanshui Palace,

415
00:19:51,870 --> 00:19:53,220
he won't let this go.

416
00:20:00,390 --> 00:20:02,220
I just hope Xiaodi stays safe.

417
00:20:02,830 --> 00:20:03,850
I'm afraid Hanshui Palace

418
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,500
won't have peace anymore.

419
00:20:13,550 --> 00:20:14,610
Get some more rest.

420
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:18,180
We should get moving.

421
00:20:18,870 --> 00:20:20,020
The pursuers will be here soon.

422
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:25,130
Head northwest.

423
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:27,220
That should lead us to West Bridge Dock.

424
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:29,330
Northwest?

425
00:20:29,790 --> 00:20:30,220
This way.

426
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:31,090
Let's go.

427
00:20:35,590 --> 00:20:36,940
I'm impressed you can

428
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:37,770
find your bearings out here.

429
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:38,980
That's not easy.

430
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,260
You're not from around here,

431
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,700
so how do you know the terrain so well?

432
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:50,260
I really don't get it.

433
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,900
You're pushing yourself this hard.

434
00:20:52,910 --> 00:20:53,740
Don't you care

435
00:20:53,740 --> 00:20:54,580
about your own life at all?

436
00:20:56,520 --> 00:20:57,460
Some things in this world

437
00:20:58,350 --> 00:20:59,570
are more important than life.

438
00:21:04,550 --> 00:21:05,700
"Love at First Sight" is acting up again?

439
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:28,050
He's the one we're ordered to capture!

440
00:21:59,390 --> 00:22:00,570
Tell Shao Jizu

441
00:22:00,710 --> 00:22:01,820
if he keeps spreading

442
00:22:01,820 --> 00:22:02,610
my portrait around,

443
00:22:02,990 --> 00:22:03,660
I won't let him off.

444
00:22:09,040 --> 00:22:09,570
Zhan.

445
00:22:40,150 --> 00:22:40,700
Wake up,

446
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:41,850
Zhan.

447
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:45,500
The horse can't keep going.

448
00:22:46,870 --> 00:22:47,970
The pursuers probably won't

449
00:22:47,970 --> 00:22:48,610
catch up anytime soon.

450
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:50,090
Let's find a place to rest.

451
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:51,260
Alright.

452
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:56,460
Are you okay?

453
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:10,020
Watch out.

454
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:23,980
Forget about me.

455
00:23:24,630 --> 00:23:25,330
Just go.

456
00:23:27,520 --> 00:23:28,940
Why are you saying that again?

457
00:23:42,380 --> 00:23:44,180
[Wanted Notice]

458
00:23:44,180 --> 00:23:45,090
Take a good look.

459
00:23:45,490 --> 00:23:46,790
I'm the one they're after,

460
00:23:46,790 --> 00:23:47,370
not you.

461
00:23:55,870 --> 00:23:56,850
See it now?

462
00:23:56,970 --> 00:23:58,560
Shao Jizu is after you,

463
00:23:58,560 --> 00:23:59,130
not me.

464
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:02,420
The prefecture troops sealed the relay stations,

465
00:24:02,420 --> 00:24:03,270
shut down every horse market,

466
00:24:03,270 --> 00:24:04,090
and are searching everywhere.

467
00:24:04,160 --> 00:24:05,090
All because of you?

468
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:08,610
You knew all along. Why didn't you tell me?

469
00:24:09,280 --> 00:24:10,740
I wasn't trying to hide it.

470
00:24:11,110 --> 00:24:11,940
You told me before

471
00:24:12,040 --> 00:24:13,030
that your friend was a constable.

472
00:24:13,830 --> 00:24:14,610
Before he died,

473
00:24:14,610 --> 00:24:15,740
he entrusted the case to you.

474
00:24:16,520 --> 00:24:17,450
That's when I figured

475
00:24:17,450 --> 00:24:18,950
even if you weren't an official,

476
00:24:18,950 --> 00:24:20,340
you still worked for the authorities.

477
00:24:20,870 --> 00:24:22,260
Shao Jizu serves the government too.

478
00:24:22,260 --> 00:24:23,420
So why is he hunting you down?

479
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:26,740
I don't know either.

480
00:24:27,150 --> 00:24:28,220
You're still not telling me the truth.

481
00:24:31,900 --> 00:24:33,010
Even if I don't exactly

482
00:24:33,010 --> 00:24:33,940
like Shao Jizu,

483
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:35,660
in this world,

484
00:24:35,750 --> 00:24:36,880
what government officer

485
00:24:36,900 --> 00:24:37,740
hunts down one of his own?

486
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:47,700
Huo...

487
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:51,020
This matter

488
00:24:51,830 --> 00:24:53,500
can no longer be judged by common sense.

489
00:24:54,590 --> 00:24:56,330
The moment I entered Xiangzhou,

490
00:24:57,630 --> 00:24:58,370
I've been constantly

491
00:24:59,110 --> 00:25:00,420
hunted by both sides of the law.

492
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:02,740
The people hunting me

493
00:25:03,450 --> 00:25:04,530
can manipulate everything

494
00:25:04,530 --> 00:25:06,130
within Xiangzhou with ease.

495
00:25:06,520 --> 00:25:07,660
They can even bring together

496
00:25:08,110 --> 00:25:09,420
Zhi Hua and the Xiuluo Cult.

497
00:25:10,770 --> 00:25:11,740
If they want to command

498
00:25:11,870 --> 00:25:13,610
Cavalry Commander Shao Jizu,

499
00:25:14,390 --> 00:25:15,810
it's entirely possible.

500
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:20,090
I can't imagine who has such power.

501
00:25:21,350 --> 00:25:22,500
I only want to know

502
00:25:23,100 --> 00:25:24,620
how someone like you escaped them.

503
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:25,290
Who are you really?

504
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,660
Who I am doesn't matter.

505
00:25:27,840 --> 00:25:28,810
At this point,

506
00:25:29,550 --> 00:25:30,900
we can't go to the capital together.

507
00:25:31,790 --> 00:25:32,670
Without me,

508
00:25:32,890 --> 00:25:33,860
it'll be much easier

509
00:25:34,350 --> 00:25:35,140
for you to escape alone.

510
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:48,180
If we leave, we leave together.

511
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:55,730
I know you

512
00:25:57,240 --> 00:25:58,660
have a righteous heart.

513
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:01,220
And that righteous heart

514
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:03,050
has earned my respect.

515
00:26:04,070 --> 00:26:04,940
But my body...

516
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:06,900
it may not hold out much longer.

517
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:13,660
So...

518
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:15,460
there's something

519
00:26:16,270 --> 00:26:17,380
I need to entrust to you.

520
00:26:18,030 --> 00:26:18,730
You mean

521
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,620
the matter your friend entrusted to you?

522
00:26:26,070 --> 00:26:26,900
His name was Liu Hongyi.

523
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:29,010
He entrusted it to me with his dying breath.

524
00:26:29,510 --> 00:26:30,570
It must be extremely important.

525
00:26:31,030 --> 00:26:32,230
Everything I've faced along the way

526
00:26:32,230 --> 00:26:33,820
only proves

527
00:26:33,820 --> 00:26:34,860
that this case

528
00:26:34,860 --> 00:26:35,740
may involve

529
00:26:35,740 --> 00:26:37,010
a massive conspiracy in Xiangzhou.

530
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:41,290
You want to stay behind

531
00:26:41,590 --> 00:26:42,810
and face the pursuers alone?

532
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:48,980
I know you won't run and save yourself.

533
00:26:50,310 --> 00:26:51,180
But this matter

534
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:52,900
concerns all of Xiangzhou.

535
00:26:53,510 --> 00:26:54,140
This letter

536
00:26:54,750 --> 00:26:55,770
must reach the capital.

537
00:26:57,790 --> 00:26:58,420
But...

538
00:26:58,830 --> 00:26:59,980
I need to warn you first.

539
00:27:00,270 --> 00:27:01,220
If you take this,

540
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:03,860
you may bring disaster upon yourself.

541
00:27:06,550 --> 00:27:07,250
I'll take it.

542
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:15,220
Don't worry.

543
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,090
This item,

544
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:18,970
I'll deliver it safely to the capital.

545
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:24,660
But once I get there,

546
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:25,360
who should I give it to?

547
00:27:26,550 --> 00:27:27,810
Since you know

548
00:27:28,310 --> 00:27:28,940
Prince Zhao,

549
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:30,570
give it to him.

550
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:32,420
Once he receives it,

551
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:33,700
he'll know what to do.

552
00:27:35,310 --> 00:27:35,730
Remember.

553
00:27:36,790 --> 00:27:37,490
From this point on,

554
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:39,490
stay out of this matter.

555
00:27:41,510 --> 00:27:42,530
What about you after I leave?

556
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,290
I'll find a way

557
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:45,250
to hold off the pursuers

558
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:47,220
and keep them from catching you.

559
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:50,050
But the road ahead...

560
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:52,810
you'll have to walk it alone.

561
00:28:00,530 --> 00:28:01,980
I haven't been honest with you.

562
00:28:02,070 --> 00:28:03,220
My real name isn't Huo Xiaodi.

563
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:06,530
You're a young hero

564
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:08,570
from Linglong Manor,

565
00:28:08,570 --> 00:28:09,700
with unmatched righteousness.

566
00:28:11,270 --> 00:28:12,400
Since you like the name

567
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:13,050
Huo Xiaodi,

568
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:15,700
then you're the only Huo Xiaodi to me.

569
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:31,810
You're acting this recklessly...

570
00:28:34,810 --> 00:28:35,660
haven't you already decided

571
00:28:35,660 --> 00:28:36,860
to fight them to the death?

572
00:28:39,590 --> 00:28:41,090
There's no way I'll die here.

573
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:43,420
I still need to live

574
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:45,050
and clear my friend's name

575
00:28:45,510 --> 00:28:46,490
while avenging him.

576
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:50,940
How are they here so fast?

577
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:20,980
How's your leg?

578
00:29:21,720 --> 00:29:22,250
I can still walk.

579
00:29:22,960 --> 00:29:24,460
But if I want to use "Glimpse of Beauty",

580
00:29:24,460 --> 00:29:25,250
I need a moment to recover.

581
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:28,180
Can you get

582
00:29:28,590 --> 00:29:29,220
up there?

583
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:30,530
No problem.

584
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:31,660
This height won't stop me.

585
00:29:32,160 --> 00:29:32,490
Good.

586
00:29:33,550 --> 00:29:34,420
We'll split up.

587
00:29:35,030 --> 00:29:35,940
Hide up there.

588
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,140
Once the pursuers enter the barn,

589
00:29:38,350 --> 00:29:39,250
I'll distract them,

590
00:29:39,390 --> 00:29:40,300
and you strike from behind.

591
00:29:41,290 --> 00:29:42,020
This group

592
00:29:42,020 --> 00:29:43,300
should be the same unit

593
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:44,250
as those cavalrymen earlier.

594
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:46,050
Handling them won't be a problem.

595
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:46,980
Okay.

596
00:29:59,510 --> 00:30:00,330
Is this spot okay?

597
00:30:01,030 --> 00:30:01,730
Stay low.

598
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:03,090
Don't let them see you.

599
00:30:09,510 --> 00:30:09,980
Huo...

600
00:30:10,550 --> 00:30:10,980
I'm sorry.

601
00:30:11,510 --> 00:30:12,250
Your pressure points

602
00:30:12,750 --> 00:30:14,220
will release in four hours.

603
00:31:33,920 --> 00:31:35,660
[Zhong Xiong, Flying-Trident Guardian]
Zhan Zhao, Southern Hero.

604
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:37,980
Your reputation is well deserved.

605
00:31:38,480 --> 00:31:39,250
Along the way,

606
00:31:39,350 --> 00:31:40,940
[Zhan Zhao, Southern Hero]
we set traps everywhere.

607
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:42,460
Thousands of elite government riders,

608
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,900
and martial heroes from every corner...

609
00:31:44,590 --> 00:31:45,560
With your portrait posted everywhere,

610
00:31:45,560 --> 00:31:46,490
we chased you for three days straight.

611
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:49,220
You almost escaped Xiangzhou too.

612
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:50,460
I can't help

613
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:51,530
but admire you.

614
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:53,290
I wondered who it was.

615
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:55,700
So it's Chief Zhong.

616
00:31:57,310 --> 00:31:57,940
You know me?

617
00:31:58,590 --> 00:32:00,010
Chief Zhong is a legendary figure.

618
00:32:00,920 --> 00:32:02,490
Who among martial artists doesn't know you?

619
00:32:02,830 --> 00:32:03,810
We're both martial artists.

620
00:32:04,590 --> 00:32:05,810
As long as you hand over that item,

621
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:07,220
I won't make things difficult.

622
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:09,530
Handing it over isn't hard.

623
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:11,700
I'm just curious

624
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:13,380
what kind of person

625
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:15,220
could bring the retired Flying-Trident Guardian

626
00:32:16,400 --> 00:32:17,460
back into the world,

627
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:19,140
and make him gather his old followers

628
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:21,860
to serve so loyally.

629
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,460
And why would Chief Zhong

630
00:32:24,550 --> 00:32:26,250
discard a martial artist's honor

631
00:32:27,270 --> 00:32:28,420
and do such dirty work?

632
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,250
Hunting down the court's pet

633
00:32:31,350 --> 00:32:32,490
counts as dirty work?

634
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:33,860
But you...

635
00:32:34,030 --> 00:32:36,220
The great Southern Hero became a lapdog of the court.

636
00:32:36,310 --> 00:32:37,810
Everyone in the martial world is talking about it.

637
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:39,480
These days, your reputation

638
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,460
isn't much better than mine.

639
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:42,980
Enough, Hero Zhan.

640
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,700
You're poisoned and dying.

641
00:32:44,790 --> 00:32:45,770
There's no way you're leaving here alive.

642
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:47,010
Hand over the item.

643
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:48,490
You'll suffer less that way.

644
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,220
If I wanted an easy life,

645
00:32:51,350 --> 00:32:52,570
I wouldn't have carried it

646
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:53,730
all the way here.

647
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:56,380
You're already at your limit.

648
00:32:56,540 --> 00:32:57,250
I wonder

649
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,730
how many moves you can still block.

650
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:02,770
How many?

651
00:33:03,750 --> 00:33:04,940
Try me and find out.

652
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:11,010
Get out.

653
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,620
Guard the barn perimeter.

654
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:13,900
Don't let him escape.

655
00:33:14,310 --> 00:33:14,810
Yes, sir!

656
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:16,860
I, Zhong Xiong,

657
00:33:17,070 --> 00:33:17,810
have always considered myself a hero.

658
00:33:18,550 --> 00:33:19,980
I've long wanted to fight the Southern Hero.

659
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:21,940
But now you're badly wounded.

660
00:33:22,480 --> 00:33:23,290
If I win,

661
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:24,940
it won't feel honorable.

662
00:33:25,120 --> 00:33:26,070
No matter how

663
00:33:26,070 --> 00:33:26,770
this battle ends,

664
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:28,700
only the two of us will know.

665
00:33:29,110 --> 00:33:30,860
Then thank you for your consideration, Chief Zhong.

666
00:33:32,350 --> 00:33:32,900
I hope

667
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:34,700
you won't regret it.

668
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:57,980
As expected of the Southern Hero.

669
00:34:58,320 --> 00:34:59,340
Even badly injured,

670
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:00,940
you still blocked so many of my attacks.

671
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:02,420
But...

672
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:04,260
if you keep fighting,

673
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:05,690
your injuries and poison

674
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:07,530
will flare up together.

675
00:35:07,710 --> 00:35:08,610
You could die on the spot.

676
00:35:09,710 --> 00:35:10,260
Chief Zhong,

677
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:12,530
do you really think you've won?

678
00:35:13,030 --> 00:35:13,780
My trident

679
00:35:14,550 --> 00:35:15,900
if it moves another inch,

680
00:35:15,900 --> 00:35:17,260
your blood will spill right here.

681
00:35:17,670 --> 00:35:18,380
What,

682
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:19,900
you think you can fly?

683
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:06,780
Is that...

684
00:36:08,630 --> 00:36:09,820
Soaring Crane Skill?

685
00:36:11,520 --> 00:36:13,460
That's the Ding family's secret art from Songjiang Prefecture.

686
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:14,850
How do you know it?

687
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,030
I told you before.

688
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:25,050
This battle...

689
00:36:26,110 --> 00:36:27,210
you'd better not regret it.

690
00:36:30,630 --> 00:36:32,130
What an incredible Soaring Crane Skill.

691
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:34,650
I, Zhong Xiong,

692
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:38,050
have witnessed a legendary martial art.

693
00:36:39,230 --> 00:36:40,490
My life was worth living after all.

694
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:43,940
I underestimated you.

695
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:45,570
The winner is decided.

696
00:36:47,110 --> 00:36:47,860
If you want to kill me,

697
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:49,530
then do it.

698
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:53,130
Killing you is easy.

699
00:36:54,510 --> 00:36:55,650
But outside this barn,

700
00:36:56,190 --> 00:36:57,740
you still have dozens of men.

701
00:36:58,550 --> 00:37:00,340
They won't let me go so easily.

702
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:02,300
Then what do you want?

703
00:37:03,590 --> 00:37:04,900
Past that farm ahead

704
00:37:05,270 --> 00:37:06,300
is West Bridge Dock.

705
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:07,650
Once I cross the river,

706
00:37:08,040 --> 00:37:10,050
I'll be outside Xiangzhou Prefecture.

707
00:37:10,470 --> 00:37:11,650
Another six miles ahead

708
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,460
and I'll reach Yincheng Town.

709
00:37:14,150 --> 00:37:15,490
The Guanghua Army is stationed there.

710
00:37:16,190 --> 00:37:17,740
Commandant Meng Kui is a friend of mine.

711
00:37:18,030 --> 00:37:18,780
He'll send men

712
00:37:18,880 --> 00:37:20,050
to escort me north.

713
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:22,290
With a fast horse,

714
00:37:22,350 --> 00:37:23,300
I can reach the capital

715
00:37:24,240 --> 00:37:25,530
in less than two days.

716
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:28,130
You want to take me hostage

717
00:37:28,440 --> 00:37:29,450
and make me escort you there?

718
00:37:37,630 --> 00:37:38,700
Not that far.

719
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,570
Just to the dock.

720
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:49,220
Move aside.

721
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:04,570
Chief Zhong,

722
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:06,380
don't move recklessly.

723
00:38:07,550 --> 00:38:09,130
Soaring Crane Skill has sealed your meridians.

724
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:11,220
If you force yourself to break free,

725
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:13,090
the backlash will kill you.

726
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:13,970
Relax.

727
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:15,420
I don't plan on dying yet.

728
00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:17,300
If I die,

729
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,340
how would I get to see

730
00:38:19,990 --> 00:38:21,220
how long your Soaring Crane Skill lasts?

731
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:41,740
You think taking me hostage

732
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:42,780
will get you safely

733
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:44,050
to the dock and onto a boat?

734
00:38:45,030 --> 00:38:45,650
The ones chasing you

735
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:48,010
aren't just my men.

736
00:38:48,630 --> 00:38:49,650
Please let us go.

737
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:01,530
Please spare my family!

738
00:39:05,080 --> 00:39:06,510
I'm begging you...

739
00:39:08,700 --> 00:39:10,660
[West Bridge Dock]

740
00:39:10,860 --> 00:39:11,920
Mother!

741
00:39:18,950 --> 00:39:20,890
Mother!

742
00:39:21,440 --> 00:39:22,490
These arrows

743
00:39:22,890 --> 00:39:24,600
are coated with Xiuluo Cult poison.

744
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:26,450
Anyone hit dies instantly.

745
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:28,800
If I were you,

746
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:31,060
I wouldn't take another step.

747
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:33,880
You're using innocent civilians as hostages?

748
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:36,570
These people

749
00:39:37,070 --> 00:39:38,530
could've lived peacefully

750
00:39:38,590 --> 00:39:40,050
at home with their families.

751
00:39:40,270 --> 00:39:41,780
They're suffering today

752
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:43,700
because of you.

753
00:39:45,590 --> 00:39:46,900
The great Southern Hero

754
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:49,450
can really stand by and do nothing?

755
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:51,650
Yan Ziqing,

756
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:54,340
the Yunying Sect was once righteous.

757
00:39:54,990 --> 00:39:56,420
Why betray your sect

758
00:39:56,990 --> 00:39:58,530
and join forces with the Xiuluo Cult?

759
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:03,490
Zhan Zhao.

760
00:40:04,470 --> 00:40:05,380
Hand over the item,

761
00:40:05,720 --> 00:40:08,140
and these people will live.

762
00:40:13,070 --> 00:40:13,740
Chief Zhong,

763
00:40:15,090 --> 00:40:16,220
today your Iron Blood Guard

764
00:40:16,360 --> 00:40:18,300
joined the Xiuluo Cult to stop me here.

765
00:40:19,030 --> 00:40:20,220
When rewards are handed out later,

766
00:40:20,800 --> 00:40:22,050
I wonder how that'll be divided.

767
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,490
In my eyes,

768
00:40:23,720 --> 00:40:24,780
only loyalty and honor matter.

769
00:40:25,360 --> 00:40:26,380
Martial world grudges,

770
00:40:26,510 --> 00:40:27,650
the rise or fall of the court...

771
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:28,570
I don't care about any of it.

772
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:30,010
If not for repaying a debt,

773
00:40:30,630 --> 00:40:32,700
I'd never work with people like them.

774
00:40:37,590 --> 00:40:39,420
Back then, Chief Zhong's River Stronghold

775
00:40:39,550 --> 00:40:41,530
was wiped out by the court,

776
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:44,010
but you never harmed the common people.

777
00:40:44,590 --> 00:40:45,300
But now,

778
00:40:46,070 --> 00:40:47,380
the benefactor you serve

779
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:48,900
has done things

780
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,480
that completely betray

781
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:51,530
everything you stand for.

782
00:40:51,990 --> 00:40:52,750
Chief Zhong,

783
00:40:52,750 --> 00:40:53,740
are you really going to ignore it?

784
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:54,900
Zhan Zhao,

785
00:40:55,070 --> 00:40:56,300
don't try to provoke me.

786
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:58,090
If you want something from me,

787
00:40:58,190 --> 00:40:59,110
just say it.

788
00:40:59,280 --> 00:40:59,860
I want to know...

789
00:40:59,860 --> 00:41:01,230
if I save them now,

790
00:41:02,470 --> 00:41:03,450
will the Iron Blood Guard

791
00:41:03,550 --> 00:41:04,530
side with Mo Dao?

792
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:05,450
Save them?

793
00:41:06,590 --> 00:41:07,380
How are you going to do that?

794
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:08,820
This is a dead end.

795
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:12,740
That's my problem.

796
00:41:14,470 --> 00:41:15,780
Chief Zhong, just tell me

797
00:41:16,510 --> 00:41:17,050
will they

798
00:41:17,590 --> 00:41:18,300
or won't they?

799
00:41:21,720 --> 00:41:22,690
I can't stand

800
00:41:22,710 --> 00:41:23,970
such despicable tactics.

801
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:26,130
Just go save them.

802
00:41:26,720 --> 00:41:27,530
The Iron Blood Guard

803
00:41:27,630 --> 00:41:28,650
won't interfere.

804
00:41:29,510 --> 00:41:30,090
But...

805
00:41:30,190 --> 00:41:31,380
we won't help you either.

806
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:32,900
Thank you.

807
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:42,550
Zhan Zhao!

808
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:43,650
Can you really bear

809
00:41:44,150 --> 00:41:45,900
to watch all these people die for you?

810
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,300
I won't let them die.

811
00:41:49,630 --> 00:41:50,490
Fine.

812
00:41:51,280 --> 00:41:52,650
Let's see

813
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:54,050
how many you can save!

814
00:41:55,590 --> 00:41:56,340
Please let us go!

815
00:41:56,440 --> 00:41:57,420
No!

816
00:41:58,320 --> 00:41:59,280
Mother!

817
00:41:59,280 --> 00:42:00,260
Please...

818
00:42:00,720 --> 00:42:02,380
Father! Mother!

819
00:43:30,860 --> 00:43:36,340
♪In this martial world, true friends are rare♪

820
00:43:37,020 --> 00:43:41,740
♪Yet some would fight by my side♪

821
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:43,900
♪Across towering mountains♪

822
00:43:43,940 --> 00:43:48,940
♪Risking all for peace beneath the heavens♪

823
00:43:49,820 --> 00:43:56,220
♪If we face life and death together, why fear the hard road ahead?♪

824
00:43:56,300 --> 00:44:02,780
♪Roaming this endless martial road♪

825
00:44:02,940 --> 00:44:09,180
♪Seeing the world's joy and sorrow pass by♪

826
00:44:09,380 --> 00:44:12,420
♪Honor still burns within us♪

827
00:44:12,540 --> 00:44:18,620
♪Still, love and grudges are the hardest to escape♪

828
00:44:18,860 --> 00:44:23,300
♪Too tangled to let go♪

829
00:44:24,820 --> 00:44:29,060
♪Who says loyalty and honor can't coexist?♪

830
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:32,740
♪One swing of the sword ends it all♪

831
00:44:33,060 --> 00:44:38,660
♪My heart stays true, just as before♪

832
00:44:39,260 --> 00:44:44,380
♪Right and wrong will reveal themselves♪

833
00:44:44,740 --> 00:44:49,620
♪Why let others decide for us?♪

834
00:44:49,860 --> 00:44:54,060
♪If this journey has no way back♪

835
00:44:54,260 --> 00:44:57,660
♪Then there's no need for sorrow♪

836
00:44:58,460 --> 00:45:04,420
♪Let a lone boat carry me past the mountains♪

837
00:45:04,860 --> 00:45:10,100
♪One last glance, and the clouds are gone♪

838
00:45:10,100 --> 00:45:15,700
♪The bright moon will light my way home♪

839
00:45:16,380 --> 00:45:23,180
♪The bright moon will light my way home♪
